name: Melevate
bio:
Let Melevate and music lift you up to new heights!

Melevate is a dynamic local DJ from San Francisco with a signature style that encompasses genres such as Progressive House, Melodic Techno, and Trance. Through her burning passion for music, Melevate turns her tunes into experiences, curating and blending genres to create an electrifying soundscape, guiding her audience on a thrilling sonic voyage.

Melevate performs at iconic SF venues such as Halcyon, 1015 Folsom, Audio, Hawthorn, Bergerac, The Phoenix Hotel, and more. Sharing the stage with Oliver Smith, Tita Lau, Tokimonsta, Audien, Zoya, Return of the Jaded, Joplyn, Robin Schulz, Jordan Suckley, and Nora Van Elken. Featured recently on the LA radio show and podcast: Global Dance Mission, Melevate's music has now even reached their worldwide audience.
